= Biding our Time

The reality is, there is not much we can do. We cannot simply do nothing either.

- @money: Raise funds.
- @dissent: Reduce party dissent.
- @campaign: Restore faith in the Republic.
- @protest: Protest against the government.
- @easy_discard

